# Mozilla Splash Page

A modern, responsive splash page for Mozilla showcasing their mission, products, and multimedia content.

## ğŸ“‹ Project Overview

This project demonstrates the implementation of a visually appealing splash page for Mozilla using HTML5 and CSS3, with a focus on multimedia integration and responsive design.

## ğŸš€ Features

- **Modern Design**: Vibrant gradient background with clean, card-based layout
- **Responsive Layout**: Adapts seamlessly to different screen sizes using flexbox and CSS grid
- **Multimedia Integration**:
  - Hero section with autoplay background video
  - Feature cards with relevant imagery
  - Product showcase with official Mozilla browser icons
  - Mission video with player controls
- **Interactive Elements**:
  - Hover effects on navigation, buttons, and cards
  - Animated social media icons
  - Smooth transitions and transformations

## ğŸ› ï¸ Technologies Used

- **HTML5**: Semantic structure with video elements
- **CSS3**: Modern styling with flexbox, grid, and animations
- **Font Awesome**: For social media icons
- **External Assets**: Mozilla official logos and videos

